<subSubSection id="9983A9D91B15FFD9FF2AFD4BFB58FE5F" pageId="11" pageNumber="522" type="biology_ecology">
<paragraph id="D126FA521B15FFD9FF2AFD4BFB58FE5F" blockId="11.[188,1394,275,584]" pageId="11" pageNumber="522">
<emphasis id="E3ED26401B15FFD9FF2AFD4BFC1AFE87" bold="true" box="[190,906,314,347]" pageId="11" pageNumber="522">Movements, Home range and Social organization.</emphasis>
The Minute Tuco-tuco is solitary. Densities are 7-42 ind/ha, and adult sex ratios are biased toward females.
</paragraph>
